<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>When the name in the From address contains a dot, the name should be enclosed in double quotes. Although the code checks a lot of characters that require the quotes ( ()&lt;&gt;[]:;@\, ), the dot is missing.</p>

<p>The fix is obvious and simple: Just add a dot to the string on line 1267 (version 1.12.1) in Zend/Mail.php.</p>

